{"id":"7456880893617823745","content":"# \\# Kemindo Group \u2013 Knowledge Base\n\n# \n\n# \\## Tentang Perusahaan\n\n# Kemindo Group adalah perusahaan multinasional yang menyediakan solusi di bidang Chemicals \\& Energy, serta Logistik untuk industri pertambangan (Mining), Pulp \\& Paper, Pertanian (Agriculture), dan Makanan (Food). Kemindo berkomitmen untuk memberikan solusi penanganan berbiaya rendah kepada pelanggan dengan produk berkualitas guna mencapai produktivitas dan efisiensi yang lebih tinggi. Kemindo bersifat customer oriented.\n\n# \n\n# PT Kemindo Cao Resources adalah pabrik manufaktur kapur (lime manufacturing factory) yang berlokasi di Sulawesi Utara. Perusahaan ini berkomitmen untuk memahami dan memenuhi kebutuhan pelanggan.\n\n# \n\n# \\### Visi \\& Misi\n\n# Menyediakan produk solusi dan layanan berkualitas kepada pelanggan dengan biaya serendah mungkin. Tujuan Kemindo adalah membantu pelanggan memaksimalkan profitabilitas mereka","embedding":[0.00464201,0.00516734,-0.017440882,-0.065748192,0.10441453,-0.048440706,0.007134359,0.024624737,-0.009510902,-0.096839055,0.006750645,0.021280466,-0.015061195,0.085029848,-0.031286929,-0.020870831,-0.048765738,-0.029299311,-0.059017383,-0.00973133,0.012622607,0.024415443,-0.012888553,-0.005166367,0.047984477,-0.034700353,0.026438864,-0.057300478,0.026375471,0.069548555,-0.067974642,-0.050761607,-0.055772234,0.126038462,-0.037310801,-0.057134774,-0.053964507,-0.002475043,0.001268536,-0.004871927,0.088613637,0.00142603,-0.086099617,0.001892859,0.008876736,0.048231076,0.054401092,0.033016227,-0.016156532,0.112526178,0.005196652,0.071473807,0.017131964,0.011872773,-0.037671182,0.004919165,0.004258019,-0.055462476,0.042743966,0.015805574,0.04027215,0.010285332,-0.049810864,-0.020058399,-0.065416068,-0.002764201,0.033898465,0.002091247,-0.026264036,-0.002693462,-0.039973006,0.004896122,-0.035719015,0.04946753,-0.007619086,-0.009424462,-0.008669187,0.015275261,0.052528933,-0.025581185,-0.039516427,0.07643012,0.01