{"id":"7456880893617823751","content":"# \n\n# \\---\n\n# \n\n# \\## Fasilitas\n\n# Kemindo memiliki fasilitas laboratorium di lokasi pelanggan (Laboratory Facilities at the Customer Site) untuk mendukung kebutuhan teknis dan quality control langsung di lapangan.\n\n# \n\n# \\---\n\n# \n\n# \\## Klien\n\n# Kemindo Group telah dipercaya oleh berbagai perusahaan besar di Indonesia, antara lain:\n\n# \\- \\*\\*RAPP\\*\\* \u2013 industri Pulp \\& Paper\n\n# \\- \\*\\*NHM\\*\\* \u2013 pertambangan\n\n# \\- \\*\\*MSM\\*\\* \u2013 pertambangan\n\n# \\- \\*\\*ANTAM\\*\\* \u2013 pertambangan\n\n# \\- \\*\\*Magotteaux\\*\\* \u2013 industri penggilingan\n\n# \\- \\*\\*Amman Mineral\\*\\* \u2013 pertambangan\n\n# \\- \\*\\*Tsingshan Steel Indonesia\\*\\* \u2013 industri baja \/ nikel\n\n# \\- \\*\\*Merdeka Tsingshan Indonesia\\*\\* \u2013 pertambangan nikel\n\n# \\- \\*\\*IMK (Indo Muro Kencana)\\*\\* \u2013 pertambangan emas\n\n# \n\n# \\---\n\n# \n\n# \\## Kontak\n\n# \n\n# \\### Indonesia\n\n# \\- \\*\\*Alamat:\\*\\* The Suites Tower, 5th Floor, Suite 3 \\& 5, Jl. Boulevard Pantai Indah Kapuk No. 1, Kav","embedding":[0.021660566,-0.002456405,-0.041651454,-0.104259938,0.119026057,-0.079380006,-0.013372781,-0.001918695,0.007798439,-0.057596918,-0.01663089,-0.026128994,-0.026113722,0.096399918,0.016802574,0.0233713,-0.027886948,0.022819003,-0.053756937,-0.013527911,0.025824308,0.029257696,0.038281746,0.014364779,0.049820416,-0.057940245,0.025848592,-0.065409355,-0.02926245,0.026223212,-0.00333752,-0.012395027,-0.039224625,0.084271982,-0.055200756,-0.01467734,0.022882018,0.005322789,-0.039848682,0.055043902,0.119042397,0.047199104,-0.092947796,-0.004135437,-0.004590917,0.026653964,-0.005036687,0.001996491,0.070938662,0.085052893,-0.029478682,0.033560254,-0.012946739,0.015046908,-0.046887882,-0.047025558,0.053864308,-0.018198643,0.060478449,-0.069017917,0.033827174,0.004350768,-0.039942,-0.04916957,-0.024684086,0.001721394,0.084196433,-0.011094801,-0.073771805,-0.037511215,-0.021