{"id":"7456889478689402883","content":"Mining \\& Coal\n\n# Kemindo memiliki 2 tambang batu bara yang berlokasi di Sumatera, saat ini melayani pelanggan di industri Pulp \\& Paper. Kemindo merupakan salah satu afiliasi grup perusahaan dengan aktivitas mulai dari produksi batu bara, feeder barge, operator, hingga manajemen stockpile.\n\n# \n\n# \\### 3. Kemindo Logistics\n\n# Motto Kemindo Logistic adalah One Stop Solution. Layanan yang tersedia meliputi:\n\n# \\- Sea Logistic (Barge \\& Vessel)\n\n# \\- Warehouse\n\n# \\- Ship to ship\n\n# \\- Trucking\n\n# \\- Layanan logistik lainnya\n\n# \n\n# \\### 4. Kemindo Green Energy\n\n# Kemindo Green Energy adalah lini bisnis yang sedang berkembang berbasis konsep biomassa, seperti Palm Kernel Shell, Coconut Shell, dan Palm Kernel Meal. Kemindo memiliki akses sebagai pembeli CPO di Dumai dengan fasilitas penyimpanan besar, serta akses ke banyak pabrik kelapa sawit dengan kontrak jangka panjang. Pabrik Kemindo di Sulawesi juga memiliki akses ke sumber Coconut Shell untuk Activated Carbon.\n\n# \n\n# \\### 5","embedding":[-0.030721072,0.000305958,-0.045564312,-0.026848471,0.075243473,-0.069050021,6.1337e-5,0.053394947,-0.013565675,-0.076032758,-0.008805186,-0.006775579,-0.032327805,0.071863502,0.023156533,0.008263476,-0.057753097,0.018871425,-0.057847124,-0.003112644,0.007277394,0.038980078,-0.03209427,0.026876943,0.051557049,-0.056724697,0.005592608,-0.047990896,-0.028090663,0.063952439,-0.0546549,-0.076256946,-0.029740235,0.118249364,-0.016843788,-0.079001211,-0.017143263,0.019488255,-0.016320871,0.058430206,0.061304346,0.006692046,-0.063053846,-0.044706043,-0.027127827,0.017253686,0.069726937,0.013909163,-0.015831824,0.076150626,0.018024495,0.067502305,-0.021361867,0.065821394,-0.053201664,0.002677666,-0.018714052,-0.009659669,0.060819078,0.001346088,0.039425127,0.02242793,-0.038602017,-0.017057898,-0.065401964,0.016988924,0.040240992,-0.021830123,-0.005698938,0.007867588,-0.056005903,-0.006226239,-0.060299274,0.06696844