{"id":"7456889628504395778","content":"Hal ini dicapai dengan menciptakan sinergi antara semua elemen rantai pasokan dan proses industri \u2014 menggabungkan keahlian, fasilitas produksi sendiri, dan jaringan yang luas untuk memenuhi kebutuhan pelanggan.\n\n# \n\n# Kemindo bertujuan menjadi yang terbaik di pasar yang dilayani, memberikan nilai tambah terbesar kepada pelanggan, pemegang saham, dan pemangku kepentingan. Operasional Kemindo menghormati regulasi termasuk keselamatan dan perlindungan lingkungan, serta berpartisipasi dalam membangun komunitas sosial yang lebih baik.\n\n# \n\n# \\---\n\n# \n\n# \\## Business Area\n\n# \n\n# \\### 1. Chemicals \\& Consumables\n\n# Kemindo menyediakan bahan kimia dan consumables untuk industri pertambangan, Pulp \\& Paper, dan berbagai industri lainnya. Kemindo bekerja sama dengan pelanggan untuk meningkatkan produktivitas dan efisiensi dengan menggabungkan kimia yang tepat, pengetahuan teknis, dan metode aplikasi yang sesuai.\n\n# \n\n# \\### 2","embedding":[0.011200855,0.001182633,-0.049202587,-0.012769721,0.086783528,-0.041157123,-0.056249414,0.002564189,-0.068247095,-0.091013968,0.039187357,-0.035572793,0.024488576,0.049005665,0.035738088,-0.000953307,-0.029201316,0.004704088,-0.036391243,0.016956918,0.02724714,0.060971424,0.004497471,0.077533916,0.020808326,-0.052509442,-0.015550909,-0.00352297,-0.009113085,0.071910068,-0.067882732,-0.084010936,-0.03304632,0.062627725,-0.018733798,-0.007346473,0.013075544,0.007339798,0.006844623,0.017482609,0.093814678,0.004406746,-0.111160144,-0.047256138,-0.024358822,0.02355892,0.029725317,0.044040468,-0.032299511,0.041250095,-0.005759637,0.071154892,0.035951816,0.021098515,-0.053632971,-0.017634716,0.030487331,0.023137949,0.045363642,0.029418571,0.030374991,0.051705062,-0.0793823,0.025791649,-0.052095186,0.018034792,0.040674899,-0.051082361,0.01388282,-0.002681556,-0.056838006,0.023450496,-0.032641493,-0.013826566,0.036351882,0.025017034,-0.016135802,-0.018369244,0.028685242,-0.02476