{"id":"7456889628504395780","content":"Kemindo Starch Plant\n\n# Kemindo merupakan yang pertama di Indonesia yang membangun pabrik 100% Green Energy melalui joint venture (JV), untuk memproduksi Native Tapioca Starch dengan kapasitas produksi di atas 15.000 ton\/bulan. Keunggulan pabrik ini:\n\n# \\- Zero waste\n\n# \\- 100% Green \\& Hygiene (dilengkapi SUS316)\n\n# \\- Peralatan pengolahan kelas dunia dari Eropa\n\n# \\- Didukung tim teknis berpengalaman\n\n# \\- Pasokan singkong telah dikonfirmasi dengan kontrak legal\n\n# \n\n# Produk unggulan: \\*\\*ECOBOND\u00ae F\\*\\* dan \\*\\*ECOBOND\u00ae B\\*\\* yang telah diterima baik di pasar.\n\n# \n\n# \\### 6. Nickel Sulfate Project (New Project)\n\n# Kemindo sedang membangun tangki penyimpanan Sulfuric Acid di Sulawesi, Indonesia dengan kapasitas 3x6.000 KL (sekitar 32.500 MT). Proyek ini merupakan bahan baku untuk baterai kendaraan listrik (EV Battery). Konsumsi awal 15.000 ton\/bulan untuk lini pertama, dengan rencana pengembangan hingga 5 lini untuk memenuhi permintaan pelanggan","embedding":[-0.025094308,0.002589437,-0.087154135,-0.028306028,0.123585954,-0.074803695,0.068419106,0.084110826,0.014954884,-0.076954953,-0.03780565,0.012877583,-0.079751089,0.079018734,-0.021774093,-0.006981581,-0.069024883,0.00551666,-0.026371168,-0.011303464,0.055799693,-0.033135328,-0.00474002,0.019248774,-0.016939608,-0.035608266,0.045377694,-0.028422566,0.024719879,0.03512226,0.02167893,-0.089600109,-0.003436331,0.129604787,-0.059320256,-0.05597904,0.015868373,0.025140274,-0.000149408,-0.032011673,0.067230903,0.026016807,-0.062071346,-0.037028,0.008613025,0.033318933,0.046108648,-0.022127785,0.007797249,0.044081446,0.019239167,0.070985198,-0.004066608,-0.006891257,-0.034375235,-0.056319658,-0.003231824,-0.014205894,0.068769462,-0.012368069,0.021355124,0.036078203,-0.016863124,-0.035555214,-0.010620198,0.025708068,0.078173406,-0.035028562,-0.038556162,-0.029226987,-0.069459394,-0.010976583,-0.022288457,0.023083927,0.019941729,0.0